description: "Map of maritime Southeast Asia, with mountains, forests and settlements represented pictorially. The lower part of the map, which had six inset maps, has been cut off and is missing."
title: "La nouvelle grande carte des Indes Orientales. Partie de la nouvelle grande carte des Indes Orientales : contenant les isles Maldives, Ceylan, Malacca, Sumatra & avec les terres adjacentes de Couchin, Negombo, Colombo & Sourabaja."
